&lt;p&gt;We are looking for an enthusiastic, organised and self-motivated person to provide administrative/secretarial support to the Associate Director of Psychological Professions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The successful candidate will be experienced in providing administrative/secretarial support to senior management, possess excellent communication skills, be proficient in the use of Microsoft Office (Word, Excel and PowerPoint) and be able to work independently using their initiative without direct supervision. They will support diary management including organising both small and large meetings.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This post is part-time (22.5 hours per week), fixed-term initially for 12 months.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
